    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="回放链接"><a href="#回放链接" class="headerlink" title="回放链接"></a>回放链接</h3><p>01.<a href="https://j86au3pdm9.pycode.haoxuexingcheng.com/share?id=+E/8wzyNTytlsL+WQuFh8JD2sIRhWApz&type=0">软件安装&amp;环境配置回放</a>  <input type="checkbox" checked style="transform:scale(1.3); accent-color: #42b983;"><br>02.<a href="https://j86au3pdm9.pycode.haoxuexingcheng.com/share?id=NGULx5fjcSwBMIOpljz8EpD2sIRhWApz&type=0">初识Python回放</a>  <input type="checkbox" checked style="transform:scale(1.3); accent-color: #42b983;"></p><p>03.<a href="https://j86au3pdm9.pycode.haoxuexingcheng.com/share?id=8E9KXWRxWoMYnCEvWoaXFZD2sIRhWApz&type=0">变量回放</a>  <input type="checkbox" checked style="transform:scale(1.3); accent-color: #42b983;"></p><p>04.<a href="https://j86au3pdm9.pycode.haoxuexingcheng.com/share?id=84kUC3prbdqj0lIHHTLRxZD2sIRhWApz&type=0">运算符回放</a>  <input type="checkbox" checked style="transform:scale(1.3); accent-color: #42b983;"></p><p>05.<a href="https://j86au3pdm9.pycode.haoxuexingcheng.com/share?id=bNmDQf6zTErm/Xf/V+2QrJD2sIRhWApz&type=0">if分支语句回放</a>  <input type="checkbox" checked style="transform:scale(1.3); accent-color: #42b983;"></p><p>06.<a href="https://j86au3pdm9.pycode.haoxuexingcheng.com/share?id=kPVLds2TMDTVzD6/Edh9ipD2sIRhWApz&type=0">循环语句回放</a>  <input type="checkbox" checked style="transform:scale(1.3); accent-color: #42b983;"></p><p>07.<a href="https://j86au3pdm9.pycode.haoxuexingcheng.com/share?id=QQ9U2L1JFqv7oiVwX90Iu5D2sIRhWApz&type=0">字符串编码回放</a>  <input type="checkbox" checked style="transform:scale(1.3); accent-color: #42b983;"></p><ul><li><a href="https://j86au3pdm9.pycode.haoxuexingcheng.com/share?id=sqYrCxKF3wd02BgH3wIF8JD2sIRhWApz&type=0">周作业1讲解回放</a>  <input type="checkbox" checked style="transform:scale(1.3); accent-color: #42b983;"></li></ul><p>08.<a href="https://j86au3pdm9.pycode.haoxuexingcheng.com/share?id=R0HLz1Ly8BIDsYf45FUuvZD2sIRhWApz&type=0">列表与元组回放</a>  <input type="checkbox" checked style="transform:scale(1.3);